task.summary: Calculate standings and games in matchday main function

Change the specification of addStandings.
Previously, addStandings required that the two arrays both have exactly the same teams; this is no longer the case. If a team exists in one standing array but not the other, the values for that team will simply be copied into the resulting array, similar to set union.
Change getLeagueGames to take a league value instead of a league key
